WEBVTT

37:06.566 --> 37:08.024
Once we understood
the whole picture,

37:08.066 --> 37:09.733
many of us in the department

37:10.274 --> 37:12.191
were on your family's side in spirit.

37:13.024 --> 37:14.108
But hey, people are human.

37:14.691 --> 37:16.399
Some hold on to their egos
and grudges.
